reviewText: Great movie for my four year old. We love everyone in Bitty Berry City!
My daughter loves Strawberry Shortcake. This is a cute addition. Only issue was the shipping and invalid charges, but Amazon customer service fixed after a few tries.
Grandchildren loved it. I'm very happy that my granddaughters love Strawberry Shortcake too--their mom's first toddler room was all Strawberry Shortcake.
My daughter loves it! Cute video and reminiscent of the original. Same complaint as I had back then - need more male characters!!
